supply and deepsea shipping for general goods and specialized cargoes   food productscavendish group produces frozen and fresh potato products and appetizers for retail quick service restaurants and food service operations throughout north america   major milestones   saint john paper millirving tissue begins with the purchase of a paper mill in saint john new brunswick this new mill produces jumbo rolls of tissue which are converted into quality consumer products     dieppe tissue plantconstruction is complete on irving tissues first tissue converting plant in dieppe new brunswick production begins for private label products and the new canadian brand majesta® is launched in canada       fort edward tissue plantirving tissue acquires a paper mill and tissue converting facility in fort edward new york irving also acquires the right to market scotties® facial tissue in the usa       toronto tissue plant irving tissue expands yet again and acquires a tissue mill and converting facility in toronto ontario irving also acquires the rights to market the royale® brand in canada       diapers  training pants irving personal care opens a new stateoftheart plant in new brunswick canada to produce premium quality private label baby diapers and training pant products for major north american retailers       tad technology major investments were made in the irving tissue plant in fort edward ny along with a building addition a new throughairdried tad paper machine is installed increasing capacity and product quality         visionto have an irving consumer product in every north american household by    purposeto delight our customers and consumers by providing quality consumer packaged goods that deliver outstanding value       values customer focussatisfy the customer every minute every hour every day   people  teamworkthe key to our success we work together with fairness and respect   quality products  servicewe meet or exceed our internal and external customers expectations 